{"tid":1761914,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"公務員要宣誓效忠政府其實另有用意? 我相信非針對一般公務員","createTime":"2019-11-29T08:17:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-29T11:36:33.000Z","uid":204245,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5991379d16ae5bb25a143926499b0272d6101367","tid":1761914,"uid":204245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T08:17:13.000Z","msg":"大家以為針對新任區議員 但其實有冇諗過未搞得成佢地就已經就任啦 我覺得反而係另有所圖<br />\n最近有種新講法 係除左建制同民主派 仲有&quot;陀槍惡曬派&quot; 亦即POPO派 <br />\n佢地連政府高官都唔畀面 光頭閪日日HI 政府 張建宗都HI<br />\nPK鄧亦做埋政府代言人 林鄭未講出聲 PK 已經講檢討唔會檢佢地 <br />\n我相信 如果... 假設最壞情況POPO 砌得低哩個運動 佢地權力將會至高無上 <br />\n所以要宣誓應該真正目的係要落金剛圏 LOCK 死POPO<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/dq-%E5%85%AC%E5%8B%99%E5%93%A1-%E7%BE%85%E6%99%BA%E5%85%89-%E5%B7%B2%E8%91%97%E6%89%8B%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E4%BB%A4%E5%85%AC%E5%8B%99%E5%93%A1%E5%AE%A3%E8%AA%93%E6%93%81%E8%AD%B7%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%B3%95/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fdq-%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258B%2599%25E5%2593%25A1-%25E7%25BE%2585%25E6%2599%25BA%25E5%2585%2589-%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E8%2591%2597%25E6%2589%258B%25E7%25A0%2594%25E7%25A9%25B6%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258B%2599%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E8%25AA%2593%25E6%2593%2581%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E5%259F%25BA%25E6%259C%25AC%25E6%25B3%2595%2F&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLWHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=3ae3b09c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fdq-%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258B%2599%25E5%2593%25A1-%25E7%25BE%2585%25E6%2599%25BA%25E5%2585%2589-%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E8%2591%2597%25E6%2589%258B%25E7%25A0%2594%25E7%25A9%25B6%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258B%2599%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E8%25AA%2593%25E6%2593%2581%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E5%259F%25BA%25E6%259C%25AC%25E6%25B3%2595%2F&h=09e0d500\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/dq-%E5%85%AC%E5%8B%99%E5%93%